      "date": "2011-03-10 14:58:34.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: Looks good to me, but someone else must approve\n\n(1 inline comment)\n\nAssuming this has been tried (my ability to check sh syntax by eye is not robust!), it looks okay to me.\n\nI've noted inline that node_name on lustre entities is probably redundant and even a bit meaningless in its current form, so it could be removed.\n\nThe important part is that Node.node_name is still set to the full domain, and that this is equal to what appears in .log filenames (maloo uses that to match up logs to hosts).  I'm taking your word for it that that's the case.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 3
    },
